{"id":280036,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-西安网友詹明松被国保约谈后被迫解散同/","date":"2013-02-20T08:45:53Z","modified":"2013-02-20T08:45:53Z","title":"维权网 | 西安网友詹明松被国保约谈后被迫解散同城QQ群（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）西安阎良网友詹明松关心时事、热心公益，是陕西同城网友聚会的积极参与者。今年参加了西安的两次同城网友聚会活动。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span><br /></span></span></div>\n<p><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span></span><span><span>年</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span></span><span><span>日</span></span><span><span>，詹明松被当地国保约谈一天，国保表示，詹明松关于朝鲜核爆污染扩散的网络言论过激，说有煽动东北人的嫌疑，他们赞赏詹明松关注弱势群体，但是告诫一些言论私下聊聊可以，不能在网上聊，要以安定团结为主，不要参与陕西同城网友聚会的活动。</span></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span></span><span><span>日</span></span><span><span>，因为持续受到当局的压力，詹明松被迫解散了他是群主的两个陕西同城网友</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span></span><span><span>群。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Pv_7gglO6Tk/USSFZbnDUoI/AAAAAAAAddg/9T27biccZCA/s1600/DSCF2162.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Pv_7gglO6Tk/USSFZbnDUoI/AAAAAAAAddg/9T27biccZCA/s400/DSCF2162.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><span></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}